Field Detail

attributes_

protected final org.xml.sax.helpers.AttributesImpl attributes_
Deprecated. 
Use this object to avoid creating a new instance of AttributesImpl on each startElement(). Make sure you call attributes_.clear() before you use it. DON'T USE THIS, for one it is not at the right place (this is a parser class, not builder) and it is still too much duplication. Instead use the attributes object in the PresentationHelper class.
